				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="BULLSHIP!: A New Spin to Liar&#039;s Dice" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>BULLSHIP! is a brand new spinoff of Liar's Dice born in Canada in which each player steps into the role of a famous notorious pirate and battle for the title of Pirate King and the legendary Black Lagoon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Player's are given five dice, two gold coins, a random character card and one barrel dice shaker. To stay alive in BULLSHIP!, you must bluff or be bluffed and use your unique character abilities to increase the odds of winning. Player's keep their dice concealed from others and make 'wages' of how many dice there are of a certain numeric value in total amongst all players. &amp;#10;e.g &amp;quot;There are 6 dice with fives in total&amp;quot; In a clockwise rotation, the next player must then increase the number of dice by at least one to continue the wager for the match. If a player believes the other player is bluffing, someone can always call &amp;quot;BULLSHIP!&amp;quot; on that active wager. When that happens, all players reveal their dice and the player who called &amp;quot;BULLSHIP!&amp;quot; either the wins the booty or loses their own booty. Once a player runs out of booty, they are eliminated and the player who defeated them steals their unique ability(s) permanently.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
